snippet.title: Dungeons & Dragons: Dark Alliance
snippet.description: Dark Alliance is Dungeons & Dragons' new action-RPG from Tuque Games coming out in fall 2020 for PCs and consoles. It features Drizzt Do'Urden and the Companions of the Hall, the first time they've starred in a D&D video game.
